        <section id="about" class="section">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>At Paiva, we specialize in garbage collection services, dedicated to empowering communities through sustainable practices and effective waste management. Our organization focuses on various initiatives aimed at enhancing the quality of life for individuals and families in our community. We believe in the power of collaboration and work closely with local leaders, volunteers, and partners to drive positive change.</p>
            <p>Our services include educational programs, environmental advocacy, and community outreach projects that aim to raise awareness about important social and environmental issues. Through our efforts, we strive to create a more informed and engaged community that is equipped to tackle challenges and seize opportunities.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="services" class="section">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <p>Paiva specializes in comprehensive garbage collection services tailored to meet the needs of our community:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Home Garbage Collection:</strong> Reliable and efficient waste collection from residential areas, ensuring a clean and healthy environment for families.</li>
                <li><strong>School Garbage Collection:</strong> Dedicated garbage collection services for schools, promoting cleanliness and sustainability in educational institutions.</li>
                <li><strong>Community Education Programs:</strong> Workshops and training sessions focused on sustainability, health, and personal development.</li>
                <li><strong>Environmental Advocacy:</strong> Promoting policies and practices that protect the environment.</li>
                <li><strong>Support for Local Initiatives:</strong> Partnering with organizations to benefit the community.</li>
                <li><strong>Recycling Programs:</strong> Facilitating recycling initiatives for responsible waste management.</li>
                <li><strong>Volunteer Opportunities:</strong> Providing programs for hands-on involvement in the community.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

